Package com.cafean.client.validation

Class PropertyContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.client.validation.ExportContext
      • com.cafean.client.validation.PropertyContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelElement, java.lang.Comparable<ExportContext>
    public class PropertyContext
extends ExportContext
    A simple export context that allows the corresponding component to be selected in the Navigator and the property to be selected in the main properties view.
    See Also:
    Navigator.expandComponentNode(AbstractModel, AbstractComponent), Navigator.setPropertyTarget(Object[], AbstractComponent[], String)
